summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2007 VOLKSWAGEN RABBIT.  THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE AIR BAG LIGHT HAS REMAINED ILLUMINATED.  HE HAS ATTEMPTED TO CONTACT THE ORIGINAL OWNER, BUT THEY HAVE YET TO RETURN HIS PHONE CALL.  HE NOTIFIED THE DEALER AND SET UP AND APPOINTMENT.  THE CONTACT STATED THAT WHEN SOMEONE IS SEATED, THE LIGHT ILLUMINATES.  HE REFERRED TO THE OWNERS MANUAL.  THE ENGINE SIZE AND POWERTRAIN WERE UNKNOWN.  THE CURRENT MILEAGE IS 4,000 AND FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 600.
